{"text_id":163456,"tokens":["This"," paper"," presents"," a"," novel"," approach"," to"," monitoring"," seismic"," activity"," and"," its"," impact"," on"," the"," Earth","'","s"," crust"," by"," utilizing"," high","-","resolution"," satellite"," imagery","."," The"," study"," focuses"," on"," the"," detection"," and"," tracking"," of"," changes"," in"," linea","ment"," structures",","," which"," are"," often"," indicative"," of"," seismic"," disturbances","."," The"," methodology"," involves"," the"," analysis"," of"," pre"," and"," post","-","earth","quake"," satellite"," images"," to"," identify"," alterations"," in"," the"," linea","ment"," patterns","."," The"," results"," demonstrate"," a"," significant"," correlation"," between"," the"," observed"," changes"," and"," the"," occurrence"," of"," earthquakes",","," thereby"," providing"," a"," potential"," tool"," for"," earthquake"," prediction"," and"," risk"," assessment","."," This"," research"," not"," only"," contributes"," to"," the"," understanding"," of"," seismic"," processes"," but"," also"," opens"," up"," new"," avenues"," for"," the"," application"," of"," remote"," sensing"," technology"," in"," geos","cience","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4","label":1}